Usage: genPinText [-help] [-format {assura dracula pvs}] [-layerMap <string>]
                  [-offset {x y}] {{[-nets <string>] [-cells <string>]} <pin_text_file>}

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
<pin_text_file>                  # <pin_text_file> (list, required)
-cells <string>                  # -cells {list of cells, or * for all}
                                 # (string, optional)
-format {assura dracula pvs}     # Specify output format (enum, optional)
-layerMap <string>               # -layerMap  layer_map_file (string, optional)
-nets <string>                   # -nets{list of nets} (string, optional)
-offset {x y}                    # Change design origin by -offset x y
                                 # (point, optional)